<!-- Navbar -->
<nav id="navbar" class="navbar fixed-bottom navbar-light bg-faded">
  <div id="container">
    <div id="pages">
      <a class="pages" href="/">Home</a>
      <a class="pages" href="/tech-gallery">Projects</a>
      <a class="pages" href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a>
      <a class="pages" href="/future">Future Plans</a>
    </div>
    <% if !session[:email] %>
      <form class="form-inline" method="POST" action="/tech-gallery">
        <div id="contact-us">contact us and sign in: </div>
        <input name="email" type="text" placeholder="Email">
        <input name="password" type="password" placeholder="Password">
        <input id="nav-submit" value="Submit" type="submit">
      </form>
    <% else %>
      <div id="logDiv">
        <button id="logout">
          <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
        </button>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    
  </div>

</nav>

<!-- Carousel -->
<div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="images/robotF.jpg" alt="First slide">
      <div id="modelZ" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Model Z</h3>
        <p>This is the first look into our current project, the Model Z. Our goal with the Model Z is to make life easier and its as simple as that. Programmed with the ability to drive and act semi human, this bot is perfect for picking up your groceries when you don't have the time, or simply to have food ready for you when you get home from work! We are designing the Model Z to perform most mundane tasks giving you the free time you deserve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="images/firstDoctorProto.jpg" alt="Second slide">
      <div id="surgical" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Fully Functioning Surgical Robot</h3>
        <p>Here we would like to show off our latest and greatest, the Sbot type 3! Type 3 is fully functional and programmed to handle over 2000 distinctive surgeries!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="images/prosthetic.jpg" alt="Third slide">
      <div id="prosthetics" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h3>Prosthetics Department</h3>
        <p>Our prosthetics deparment here at Shepard Robotics is top of the line, every day we make strides to have our prosthetics looking more and more realistic, as well as giving them full functionality. Our goal is to free the minds of those with physical handicaps and we beleive we make a difference every day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
